                type="document" xml:id="d424">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>The only source found for this conversation is the following informal note by
                    Harriman: <quote rend="blockquote">
                        <p>“Had a talk with Eden about Russia and the proposed discussion, and the
                                agenda.”<note n="1" xml:id="d424fn1">The reference is apparently to
                                the proposed tripartite meeting at the Foreign Ministers level. For
                                further background on this conference, which was convened at Moscow
                                in October 1943, see <ref target="frus1943v01#pg_513">
                                    <hi rend="italic">Foreign Relations</hi>, 1943, vol. <hi
                                        rend="smallcaps">i</hi>, pp. 513</ref> ff.</note> (Harriman
                            Papers)</p>
                    </quote>
                </p>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
